# PMIC RTC class/drivers configuration
#

config RTC_SAMSUNG_PMIC
	tristate "Samsung PMIC COMMON RTC"
	depends on I2C
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  RTC of Samsung PMIC series.
	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called pmic-rtc.

config RTC_DRV_S2MPS25
	tristate "Samsung PMIC S2MPS25 RTC"
	depends on MFD_S2MPS25
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  RTC of Samsung PMIC series.
	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called rtc-s2mps25.

config RTC_DRV_S2MPS25_9935
	tristate "Samsung PMIC S2MPS25 RTC for 9935"
	depends on MFD_S2MPS25_9935
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  RTC of Samsung PMIC series.
	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called rtc-s2mps25.

config RTC_DRV_S2MPU15_8535
	tristate "Samsung PMIC S2MPU15 RTC for 8535"
	depends on MFD_S2MPU15_8535
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  RTC of Samsung PMIC series.
	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called rtc-s2mps25.

config RTC_DRV_S2MPU15_8835
	tristate "Samsung PMIC S2MPU15 RTC for 8835"
	depends on MFD_S2MPU15_8835
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  RTC of Samsung PMIC series.
	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called rtc-s2mps25.
